messages.subject: Going no-mail
messages.msgSnippet: I am going no-mail for a while or I ll never get my script finished. The list is too interesting and sucks up my time. I have no capacity to resist temptation
messages.messageBody:
I am going no-mail for a while or I'll never get my script finished. The
list is too interesting and sucks up my time. I have no capacity to
resist temptation and not check my mail. In reality I probably won't
check the lists very often either, however I will return, well before
the SC conference. If for some reason that eludes me completely at the
moment anyone should want to speak to me, my email address is available.
In closing I would like to add that I was watching "Bridget Jones Diary"
last night and Colin Firth is still the top of my list of Doable.

Robyn Coburn
